Download RedAlert1_SovietDisc.rar and RedAlert1_AlliedDisc.rar
from http://www.commandandconquer.com/classic


Put the following files in this directory

RedAlert1_AlliedDisc/RedAlert1_AlliedDisc/CD1_ALLIED_DISC.ISO:
INSTALL/REDALERT.MIX as REDALERT.MIX
MAIN.MIX as MAIN.MIX

RedAlert1_SovietDisc/RedAlert1_SovietDisc/CD2_SOVIET_DISC.ISO:
MAIN.MIX as RUSSIAN.MIX

